In addition to becoming the leader in micro-investing, Acorns is dedicated to more humanitirian goals, such as teaching people about investing and personal finance and planting oak trees to fight climate change. Acorns offers a very extensive, easy to read Q&A on finanical terms as part of their website and is integrated into their app. Acorns has also partnered with One Tree Planted to plant 438,000 oak trees to date.[1]


